headline: Emerson Electric (EMR): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Emerson Electric trades at $114.65 per share and has stayed on track with the overall market, gaining 5.3% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 was flat.
